CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 15, reads: "OES Recital - Omega Vesper Choir of Omega Grand Chapter, OES, presented Mrs. Mollie Johnson Lewis, second from left, in a recent recital at John Wesley AME Zion Church. Others in picture are, left to right, Mrs. Esther Green, Worthy Grand Matron; Mrs. Louise Kellum, Grand Organist, and Mrs. Edmonia Stevens, Grand Directness. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of eight men, and nineteen women, including Louise Kellum on left, Edmonia Stevens fifth from left, followed by Mollie Johnson Lewis and Esther Green, posed in John Wesley AME Zion Church
